Title: The End of a Priest
Actors: Vlastimil Brodský, Jan Libícek, Jana Brejchová, Zdena Skvorecka
Plot: A verger, who likes to dress as a priest, is invited, by one of the villagers, to be the pastor at a vacant church. The atheist teacher resents the pastor, and tries to embarrass him in various ways, including being caught with the local girl, Majka.
